{"tid":1309742,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"新證據，證眀想推[社會信用體系統]","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T17:54:32.000Z","uid":167961,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5a68ac0ba8a7881b1ed4475c1cba8e062d68bdb1","tid":1309742,"uid":167961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"除咗起智能燈柱同換RFID身份證， 林鄭仲喺2017司政報告度提出2020年起用eID(電子身份證)，除咗應用喺政府服務，竟然想應用埋落銀行同商業網上交易度！咁就大獲啦，到時政府就可以有曬我哋嘅大少交易紀錄，銀行戶口存款、轉帳記錄，海外開戶記錄同埋信用評級。啫係我哋嘅所有交易都會變曬實名制，落曬政府紀錄度！<br />\n<br />\n而且認證過程需要市民下載手機應用程式，上載由手機拍攝身份證相片，再面向手機前鏡眨眼兩次，與入境處資料即時對比，通過核對，從此就會將eID綁定於申請手機中，只要追蹤你嘅手機就可以知道你嘅位置，你嘅手機就係追蹤器。<br />\n<br />\n杭州喺2018年4月一開始推行社會信用體系嘅時候，都首先喺支付寶開通「電子身份證」功能，用戶需要「刷臉」綁定帳戶，連通公安部的CTID認證平台,將手機同個人身分綑綁。再透過5G極速，配合全國2億部CCTV及每一家每一戶的智能電器，公安只需在電腦一按，就可以追蹤每一張臉的實時位置，即時顯示對象現時的評分、最近行為和足跡、戶口結餘、居住地址、最新發出的短訊內容、購買紀錄等等。<br />\n<br />\n政府喺起燈柱有曬所有人即時定位之後，仲需要市民手機IP、戶口資料、消費紀錄，所以極有理由相信推行eID都係為咗攞倒我哋呢啲資料，為全面推行社會信用系統撘路。"},{"pid":"6494319374a934f751acecdcbf97500fb0f7904b","tid":1309742,"uid":251086,"like":4,"dislike":43,"score":-39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"Big data 係大趨勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a441c7ba0f9a98a79b6547ebcba3592edcc4af8c","tid":1309742,"uid":167961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"Reference:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/economy/article/2115365/hong-kong-launch-new-electronic-identification-part-smart\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Feconomy%2Farticle%2F2115365%2Fhong-kong-launch-new-electronic-identification-part-smart&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=6bef737e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/economy/article/2115365/hong-kong-launch-new-electronic-identification-part-smart</a><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2323786/%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E7%B4%84400%E6%94%AF%20%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2323786%2F%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%25A8%2599%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%259D%25E7%25B4%2584400%25E6%2594%25AF%2520%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2588%25E6%259F%25B1%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=f59bab2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2323786/%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E7%B4%84400%E6%94%AF%20%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ourhkfoundation.org.hk/innotechexpo2018/zhihuishimindeshumagerenshenfen-eid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fourhkfoundation.org.hk%2Finnotechexpo2018%2Fzhihuishimindeshumagerenshenfen-eid&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=a9e3d92e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ourhkfoundation.org.hk/innotechexpo2018/zhihuishimindeshumagerenshenfen-eid</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2525251037525019?s=100000426330841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F972393926144079%2Fposts%2F2525251037525019%3Fs%3D100000426330841&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=483537c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2525251037525019?s=100000426330841</a>"},{"pid":"d6159f645e29279517ca138ab36a0e69141641f4","tid":1309742,"uid":167961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6494319374a934f751acecdcbf97500fb0f7904b","tid":1309742,"uid":251086,"like":4,"dislike":43,"score":-39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"Big data 係大趨勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"係 但連落銀行同其他交易度係咪必要，同埋港共政府一啲誠信都冇度真係信唔過啲資料落入佢地手中"},{"pid":"aceb4c18c6f94f2ab2aeeab0241eb5b03cee1d46","tid":1309742,"uid":167961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"大家齊抵制eID<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a9e5b2b2a5f7e68fd7039807f24c5f78b1538b","tid":1309742,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"佢喺control freak"},{"pid":"9a1f44e7b00b477e70f4c8f7c5b875805906b6b3","tid":1309742,"uid":45910,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"你班仆街俾我抖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aede56223f5e36b6715032c27297ff3d6662e98","tid":1309742,"uid":167961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a9e5b2b2a5f7e68fd7039807f24c5f78b1538b","tid":1309742,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"佢喺control freak"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"唔想成為信用系統分數奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2cc8dc88623f4b519d9771145af190b05f9545","tid":1309742,"uid":167961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a1f44e7b00b477e70f4c8f7c5b875805906b6b3","tid":1309742,"uid":45910,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"你班仆街俾我抖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/